<div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-[#1f2937] border border-[#374151] rounded-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 shadow-xl">
  <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
    <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-[var(--brand)] shadow-lg shadow-[var(--brand-soft)] text-white flex items-center justify-center bg-[var(--card)]">
      <span class="text-3xl font-black text-[var(--brand)]">W</span>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[var(--brand)] text-black p-1 rounded-full border-2 border-[#1f2937] shadow-sm">
      <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-grow text-center md:text-left">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Editorial Team</h3>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-[var(--brand-soft)] text-[var(--brand)] border border-[var(--brand)]/20">
        Verified Authority
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
      The CoursesWyn Editorial Team is dedicated to providing verified Udemy promo codes and savings guides. Our experts monitor thousands of course vouchers daily to ensure you get the best educational value for your money.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
      <a href="mailto:admin@courseswyn.com" class="text-xs font-bold text-[var(--brand)] hover:text-white flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
        Contact Editorial Team
      </a>
      <span class="text-gray-600 text-xs hidden md:inline">•</span>
      <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic">Verified by CoursesWyn Editorial Team</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
